      • Gameboard

        public Gameboard(LevelType levelType,
                 Level level,
                 Style style,
                 java.util.ArrayList<PlayerProfile> profiles)
          throws java.io.IOException,
                 java.lang.ClassNotFoundException,
                 java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException,
                 java.lang.NullPointerException
        Creates a Gameboard from a Level Path, Style and a Collection of PlayerProfile
        Parameters:
        level - Level to create a board from
        style - Style of the board
        profiles - Collection of PlayerProfile of the players
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If the Level file could not be found.
        java.lang.ClassNotFoundException - If a class in the Level file could not be found
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - If a tiles coordinate doesn't exist in the Gameboard Matrix
        java.lang.NullPointerException - If there aren't enough tiles to be placed on the gameboard
